{"word":"G4363 - προσπίπτω - prospíptō - pros-pip'-to - Beat upon","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προσπίπτω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">prospíptō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pros-pip'-to</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Beat upon</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - மோது, விழு"},{"paragraph":"1. to fall toward, fall upon"},{"paragraph":"2. to rush upon, beat against"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4314 - πρός - prós - pros/4314\">G4314</a> and <a href=\"#/G4098 - πίπτω - píptō - pip'-to/4098\">G4098</a>; to <i>fall towards</i>, that is, (gently) <i>prostrate</i> oneself (in supplication or homage), or (violently) to <i>rush</i> upon (in storm): - beat upon, fall (down) at (before).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}